      "content": "oxygenation optimization? i havent heard of that before. sounds a bit intense though. i was actually thinking maybe my controller inhaler just isn't working as well as it used to. do you think i should just take more of it when i feel this way? like maybe double the dose if i'm really struggling to catch my breath?",
